item.title: Ok well help
item.dc:creator: @BurnInSilence BurnInSilence
item.description:
@BurnInSilence wrote:

left click the ladder
get its object #
search for in client.java
case #:
replace # with the object id
you should see

teleportToX = ####; teleportToY = ####; heightLevel += 1
change the teleport coords to where you want to go
if all you see is

heightLevel += 1

then add

teleportToX = ####; teleportToY = ####;
substituting with your own coords
